      • CommandList

        public CommandList(int[] priorities,
                   MyDate[] start,
                   MyDate[] end,
                   OptionType[] options)
        Creates a new instance of this command with the list of field values to use for filtering and the list of options to use for sorting the filtered list.
        Parameters:
        keywords - The list of keywords used to filter items or null if unused.
        priorities - The priority levels used to filter items or null if unused.
        start - The list of start date values used to filter the items or null if unused.
        end - The list of end date values used to filter the items or null if unused.
        options - The list of options(in decreasing precedence) used to sort the filtered list or null if unused.
